submission_title: Student newspaper: Students raise concerns over UTSU changes to mental health coverage
author: the-varsity

submission_title: Student newspaper: Students raise concerns over UTSU changes to mental health coverage
author: crud_lover
body:
"In an email to The Varsity on September 22, Shechtman wrote that the union will have a meeting with its health and dental service provider, and that they are looking into other options to support students."


Glad to hear this. I'd gladly apply for this new subsidy if I didn't have to submit sensitive information through a Google Form run by UTSU.
